name: [22/24] Secrets of Osaka - Sleepless
description:
"Rain stopped. You waited until the sun goes up again. You slowly wander back home. So much experienced in these days." 

Twentysecond picture of the 24 Days NFT Photography Adv(HEN)t Series. Secrets of Osaka's Sidealleys and Streets. Showing the exact coordinates of the Location the Photo was shot. I can't believe we are near the end. Two to go.
